{"tid":922618,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高圖爾斯：若離開車路士必帶走夏薩特","createTime":"2018-11-30T14:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T14:27:21.000Z","uid":112702,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80f47a41043c83e598e81abd3333a6d660605227","tid":922618,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"「我在車路士很開心，不一定會離開。在車路士度過了6年之後，也許是時候尋找一些不同的東西了。我可以決定我是留下還是離開，車路士也會作出最終決定，如果他們想賣掉我的話，你知道我的首選目的地（皇家馬德里）。」<br />\n<br />\n「無論我去哪裡，夏薩特都必須跟我走，我們不會讓彼此離開對方。」高圖爾斯補充說道。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d7688d29baa0a42031a705f1a01bfa42934089","tid":922618,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"而家車路士出副選都打得殘隊濕鳩黃狗<br />\n冇左牙朗根本三線球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa712dd57cba814719bc60fbf6c4ca4b6c77315","tid":922618,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d7688d29baa0a42031a705f1a01bfa42934089","tid":922618,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"而家車路士出副選都打得殘隊濕鳩黃狗<br />\n冇左牙朗根本三線球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"牙油hoball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}